data.description: Discover your dream home in Round Lake Beach with this impressive ranch, showcasing a tastefully remodeled kitchen, complete with spacious cabinets, and a stylish center island. The large living room features shiplap paneling, and the three bedrooms on the first floor offer plenty of natural light. Two-additional bedrooms in the full-finished English basement with a large family/recreation room. Bring your ideas to use all this space! 2.5 Detached car garage features a brand new garage door, a 20 amp electric box. Front yard and back yard are fully fenced. Trampoline and kid's swings stay with the sale. Grayslake schools- Come and see this beautiful home today!
